title: New York Rye Bread
ingredients: ['250ml (9 fl oz) warm water', '1 1/3 tablespoons vegetable oil', '2 tablespoons honey', '1 teaspoon salt', '2 2/3 teaspoons caraway seed', '150g (5 oz) rye flour', '300g (11 oz) bread flour', '1 oz vital wheat gluten (gluten flour)', '4 tablespoons dried milk powder', '2 1/2 teaspoons dried active baking yeast']
